20people%20to%20avoid%20major%20retailers%20and%20call%20out%20from%20work%20if%20possible.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20remains%20unclear%20how%20many%20are%20engaged%20in%20boycotting%20and%20what%20the%20impacts%20may%20be.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2028%2C%20protestors%20aligned%20with%20a%20grassroots%20organization%20called%20the%20People's%20Union%20USA%20plan%20to%20hold%20an%20economic%20blackout%20targeted%20at%20corporations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCorporations%20and%20banks%20only%20care%20about%20their%20bottom%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20People's%20Union%20USA%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewebsite%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20disrupt%20the%20economy%20for%20just%20ONE%20day%2C%20it%20sends%20a%20powerful%20message.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20whole%20day%20on%20February%2028%2C%20the%20organization%20calls%20on%20people%20to%20refuse%20to%20make%20purchases%20online%20or%20in-store%20from%20major%20retailers%20or%20spend%20money%20on%20gas%20or%20fast%20food.%20If%20spending%20is%20necessary%2C%20the%20People's%20Union%20suggests%20buying%20from%20small%20businesses%20only%20and%20using%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20one%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20website%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20we%20show%20them%20who%20really%20holds%20the%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effort%20is%20spearheaded%20by%20John%20Schwarz%2C%20who%20described%20himself%20on%20the%20website%20as%20%26quot%3Bjust%20a%20man%20who%20has%20lived%20through%20struggle%2C%20seen%20the%20truth%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20system%20is%20designed%20to%20keep%20all%20of%20us%20trapped%2C%26quot%3B%20Schwarz%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20I%20started%20this%20organization.%20Because%20I%20believe%20we%20deserve%20better.%20Because%20I%20believe%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20break%20free%20from%20a%20system%20built%20to%20exploit%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchwarz%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20People's%20Union%20USA%20also%20plans%20longer%20and%20more%20focused%20boycotts%20down%20the%20road%2C%20including%20a%20weeklong%20boycotts%20against%20Amazon%2C%20Nestle%2C%20and%20Walmart%20in%20March%20and%20April.%20The%20organization%20also%20called%20on%20people%20to%20take%20Friday%20off%20from%20work%2C%20if%20they%20are%20able%20to%20do%20so%20without%20risking%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20unclear%20how%20many%20people%20are%20committed%20to%20boycotting%20the%20economy%20on%20Friday%20and%20what%20kind%20of%20impact%20it%20may%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20some%20boycotts%20have%20had%20short-lived%20or%20even%20counterintuitive%20effects.%20When%20there%20were%20calls%20to%20boycott%20Goya%20after%20the%20company's%20CEO%20praised%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20in%202020%2C%20the%20company%20later%20said%20sales%20actually%20increased%20thanks%20to%20Trump%20supporters%20initiating%20a%20counter-movement%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bbuycott%26quot%3B%20that%20encouraged%20people%20to%20buy%20from%20Goya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsight.kellogg.northwestern.edu%2Farticle%2Fcompany-boycott-buycott-impact%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Kellogg%20School%20of%20Management%20at%20Northwestern%20University%20found%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bbuycott%20effect%20overwhelmed%20the%20boycott%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20temporarily%20raising%20the%20company's%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20other%20boycotts%20may%20have%20been%20more%20effective%20depending%20on%20the%20cause%20that%20mobilized%20people%20to%20boycott.%20In%202023%2C%20Bud%20Light%20faced%20fierce%20conservative%20backlash%20after%20a%20brief%20branding%20stint%20with%20a%20transgender%20influencer.%20Well%20over%20one%20year%20later%2C%20sales%20for%20Anheuser-Busch%2C%20which%20makes%20Bud%20Light%2C%20remained%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomic-blackout-boycott-protest-feb-28-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740682291000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0a6b3b8b41a9673f93231%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomic-blackout-boycott-protest-feb-28-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Protesters%20are%20planning%20an%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20blackout%26quot%3B%20for%20Feb.%2028%2C%20and%20are%20calling%20for%20consumers%20to%20boycott%20major%20retailers%20for%20one%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbalevic%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Balevic)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomic-blackout-boycott-protest-feb-28-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Drove%20Away%20After%20His%20Car%20Hit%20Indian%20Student%20In%20US%3A%20Cops%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20whose%20car%20hit%20Indian%20student%20Nilam%20Shinde%20in%20California%20on%20February%2014%20drove%20away%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20leaving%20the%20severely%20injured%20woman%20behind.%2058-year-old%20Lawrence%20Gallow%20was%20arrested%20five%20days%20later%20on%20February%2019%2C%20the%20Sacramento%20Police%20Department%20told%20NDTV%20on%20Thursday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bhit-and-run%20collision%26quot%3B%20was%20reported%20from%20Fair%20Oaks%20Blvd%20and%20Cadillac%20Dr%20in%20Sacramento%20just%20before%207%20pm%2C%20the%20police%20said.%20When%20the%20officers%20reached%20the%20location%2C%20they%20found%20Ms%20Shinde%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResponding%20officers%20located%20a%20female%20adult%20on%20the%20ground.%20The%20vehicle%20involved%20in%20the%20collision%20fled%20the%20scene%20prior%20to%20police%20arrival