Cp%3ERen%C3%A9e%20Reizman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22201711fb-dc91-4d90-903e-e36e50656b4c%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20murder%20caused%20chaos%20in%20the%20mansion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20successfully%20completed%20the%20challenge%2C%20but%20our%20celebrations%20were%20cut%20short%20when%20our%20guide%20announced%20it%20was%20time%20for%20the%20first%20murder.%20We%20circled%20up%2C%20and%20the%20Faithfuls%20put%20their%20eye%20masks%20back%20on.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20one%20other%20Traitor%2C%20and%20our%20guide%20asked%20us%20to%20point%20to%20who%20we%20wanted%20to%20kill.%20Without%20a%20private%20turret%20like%20the%20TV%20show%2C%20our%20sudden%20decision%20couldn't%20be%20strategized%20or%20discussed.%20We%20pointed%20toward%20another%20player%20at%20random.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20felt%20terrible%20because%20I%20was%20worried%20that%20our%20murdered%20player%20would%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20experience.%20It%20turned%20out%20that%20he%20could%20continue%20participating%2C%20just%20with%20some%20disadvantages.%20My%20guilty%20conscience%20was%20wiped%20clean.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d68345a-c51f-4649-881c-abeb0dcdf0a4%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20game%20continued%20with%20more%20challenges%20and%20a%20recruitment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223780%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lasers%20in%20a%20space%20with%20pedestals%20with%20sclptres%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c08a9f69253ccddf97c4c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20challenge%20felt%20like%20a%20nod%20to%20season%20two%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Traitors.%26quot%3B%20%3Cp%3ERen%C3%A9e%20Reizman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20entered%20the%20next%20room%20and%20saw%20%26quot%3Bpriceless%26quot%3B%20artifacts%20on%20pedest