le%20than%20the%20popular%20%24190%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforme-power-bra-review-taylor-swift-eras-tour-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForme%20posture-correcting%20bra%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20seemed%20less%20clunky%20than%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbetter-back-review-shark-tank%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eback%20belt%20or%20brace%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20using%20the%20device%20for%20two%20weeks%2C%20I%20quickly%20changed%20some%20poor%20posture%20habits.%20I%20plan%20to%20keep%20wearing%20it%2C%20even%20though%20fixing%20my%20back%20issues%20will%20take%20more%20than%20a%20posture%20corrector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c199d1fb-93f8-4c8d-8801-4446be2dc2e6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20learned%20I%20was%20slouching%20even%20more%20than%20I%20realized%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20graphic%20of%20a%20person%20slouching%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67858b61e294a7514e8cdcac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221563%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20device%20buzzes%20until%20I%20get%20back%20into%20the%20green%20zone.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%2FUpright%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Upright%20was%20easy%20to%20charge%20and%20set%20up.%20After%20downloading%20the%20app%2C%20I%20was%20prompted%20to%20calibrate%20the%20device%20to%20my%20upright%20posture%20to%20establish%20a%20baseline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20I%20would%20get%20a%20reminder%20a%20few%20times%20an%20hour%2C%20but%20it%20was%20more%20like%20a%20few%20times%20every%20five%20minutes.%20The%20moment%20I%20started%20getting%20remotely%20engrossed%20in%20my%20work%2C%20the%20soft%20buzz%20along%20my%20spine%20brought%20me%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%20I%20readjusted%20the%20height%20of%20my%20desk%20that%20it%20became%20easier%20to%20stay%20straighter%20%E2%80%94%20my%20default%20position%20was%20hunched%20over%20to%20begin%20with.%20For%20getting%20me%20to%20notice%20and%20make%20that%20tiny%20adjustment%20alone%2C%20the%20Upright%20was%20worth%20it.%20My%20lower%20back%20also%20felt%20a%20little%20sore%2C%20which%20seemed%20promising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282a4ab32-a445-4694-a7b4-edcd48ee2ce6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20harder%20to%20use%20during%20deep%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22567%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20graph%20of%20posture%20improvement%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67858ba48951662c9f1ff14f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22410%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20posture%20dips%20when%20I%20focus.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20focused%20I%20get%20on%20a%20work%20assignment%2C%20the%20more%20my%20spine%20curls%20like%20a%20shrimp%20in%20a%20hot%20pan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20into%20an%20annoyingly%20vicious%20cycle%3A%20I'd%20fixate%20on%20writing%20or%20editing%20a%20story%20and%20start%20to%20slouch%2C%20setting%20off%20the%20device.%20I'd%20lose%20my%20train%20of%20thought%2C%20straighten%20up%2C%20and%20start%20over.%20Then%2C%20I'd%20get%20another%20buzz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20got%20to%20the%20point%20where%20I%20had%20to%20remove%20the%20necklace%20to%20work%20on%20anything%20that%20required%20my%20sustained%20attention.%20I%20found%20it%20easiest%20to%20keep%20the%20Upright%20on%20when%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20actively%20type%2C%20such%20as%20during%20work%20calls%20or%20doing%20errands%20around%20the%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20Lees%2C%20director%20of%20chiropractic%20operations%20at%20The%20Joint%20Chiropractic%20in%20New%20York%2C%20recommended%20wearing%20the%20device%20six%20to%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%20to%20properly%20form%20a%20habit.%20I%20was%20averaging%2C%20at%20most%2C%20two%20to%20three.%20I%20also%20didn't%20wear%20it%20out%20socializing%20because%20I%20wanted%20a%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20demonstrates%20an%20issue%20that%20Dr.%20Arun%20Hariharan%2C%20a%20board-certified%20pediatric%20orthopedic%20and%20spine%20surgeon%20specializing%20in%20scoliosis%2C%20told%20me%3A%20smart%20devices%20are%20only%20as%20good%20as%20your%20commitment%20to%20them.%20%26quot%3BThose%20are%20great%20tools%20to%20understand%20what's%20going%20on%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20the%20fix%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20other%20health%20devices%20like%20fitness%20rings%20and%20sleep%20trackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Upright%20revealed%20how%20often%20I%20slouch%2C%20but%20solving%20the%20issue%20is%20more%20complicated%20than%20wearing%20a%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20science%20behind%20smart%20posture%20correctors%20isn't%20substantive%2C%20said%20Hariharan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20plays%20almost%20no%20role%20in%20our%20medical%20treatment%20because%20the%20evidence%20hasn't%20been%20strong%20enough%20to%20recommend%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20While%20some%20people%20credit%20the%20devices%20for%20helping%20them%20improve%20their%20habits%2C%20the%20long-term%20impact%20is%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226720a9fe-79dd-4aa7-8e93-9d7515a09a01%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoctors%20say%20I%20can%20do%20more%20for%20my%20spine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20news%20is%20that%20outside%20medical%20conditions%20like%20scoliosis%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20can%20reverse%20a%20lot%20of%20poor%20posture%20in%20six%20to%2012%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Lees%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20using%20the%20Upright%2C%20Lees%20recommended%20wearing%20posture-correcting%20sports%20bras%20or%20braces%20for%20short%20intervals%2C%20such%20as%20when%20I'm%20exercising%2C%20to%20form%20better%20habits%20while%20moving.%20The%20goal%20is%20for%20me%20to%20eventually%20not%20need%20them%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20stiffness%2C%20Lees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http