ts%20state-owned%20natural%20resource%20revenues%20to%20a%20fund%20dedicated%20to%20invest%20in%20Ukraine.%20Notably%2C%20this%20deal%20does%20not%20include%20any%20U.S.%20security%20guarantees.%20On%20paper%2C%20the%20U.S.%20appears%20poised%20to%20reap%20significant%20benefits%20from%20this%20agreement%2C%20considering%20Ukraine's%20natural%20resources%20and%20environment%20ministry%20claims%20that%20the%20country's%20bedrock%20contains%20approximately%205%25%20of%20the%20world's%20critical%20raw%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20resources%2C%20including%20graphite%2C%20lithium%2C%20titanium%2C%20beryllium%2C%20and%20uranium%2C%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20production%20of%20batteries%2C%20radar%20systems%2C%20and%20armour%2C%20which%20are%20essential%20to%20the%20defence%20and%20tech%20industries.%20Securing%20access%20to%20these%20resources%20could%20help%20reduce%20America's%20reliance%20on%20Chinese%20minerals.%20However%2C%20the%20actual%20extent%20of%20Ukraine's%20mineral%20wealth%20remains%20a%20mystery%2C%20with%20only%20around%208%2C000%20of%20the%20country's%2020%2C000%20surveyed%20mineral%20deposits%20and%20sites%20deemed%20viable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20these%20resources%20is%20further%20complicated%20by%20the%20need%20for%20significant%20investment%2C%20estimated%20at%20%2415%20billion%20for%20the%2010%20largest%20known%20mining%20prospects.%20This%20includes%20the%20construction%20of%20mines%2C%20quarries%2C%20and%20processing%20facilities.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20extraction%20process%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20costly%20and%20time-consuming%2C%20with%20the%20Ukrainian%20Geological%20Survey%20estimating%20that%20developing%20the%20Novopoltasvke%20deposit%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20rare%20earth%20sites%20in%20the%20world%2C%20would%20require%20an%20investment%20of%20%24300%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20currently%20dominates%20the%20rare%20earth%20supply%20chain%2C%20processing%20nearly%2090%25%20of%20the%20world's%20rare%20earths.%20The%20U.S.%20and%20other%20major%20producers%20lack%20the%20necessary%20infrastructure%20and%20expertise%20to%20refine%20these%20minerals%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20rely%20on%20Beijing.%20Developing%20this%20infrastructure%20in%20Ukraine%20would%20take%20years%20and%20likely%20be%20less%20efficient%20than%20shipping%20the%20minerals%20to%20China%20for%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20is%20also%20complicated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20several%20promising%20mineral%20prospects%20are%20located%20in%20territories%20under%20Russian%20occupation.%20Ukrainian%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Yulia%20Svyrydenko%20estimates%20that%20Russia%20has%20occupied%20%24350%20billion%20worth%20of%20Ukraine's%20critical%20mineral%20and%20gas%20reserves.%20Trump%20must%20now%20decide%20whether%20to%20increase%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20and%20help%20the%20country%20reclaim%20its%20occupied%20territories%20or%20pursue%20an%20alternative%20deal%20with%20Russia.%20As%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20notes%2C%20extracting%20Ukraine's%20rare%20earth%20elements%20might%20not%20be%20profitable%20due%20to%20the%20technical%20challenges%20and%20costs%20involved.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740680700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fef85092o_donald-trump-reuters_625x300_27_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-donald-trump-might-be-on-the-losing-end-of-the-mineral-deal-with-ukraine-7809669%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump%20must%20now%20decide%20whether%20to%20increase%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20and%20help%20the%20country%20reclaim%20its%20occupied%20territories%20or%20pursue%20an%20alternative%20deal%20with%20Russia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-donald-trump-might-be-on-the-losing-end-of-the-mineral-deal-with-ukraine-7809669%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22