p_articleshow%2F118610571.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Cuts%20Overseas%20Development%20Program%20Budgets%20By%20More%20Than%2090%25%3A%20State%20Dept%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20dramatically%20cut%20the%20budgets%20of%20overseas%20development%20and%20aid%20programs%2C%20with%20multi-year%20contracts%20pared%20down%20by%2092%20percent%2C%20or%20%2454%20billion%2C%20the%20State%20Department%20said%20Wednesday.%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20his%20first%20day%20in%20office%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20demanding%20a%20freeze%20on%20all%20US%20foreign%20aid%20for%2090%20days.%20The%20pause%20aimed%20to%20allow%20the%20administration%20to%20review%20overseas%20spending%20with%20an%20eye%20to%20gutting%20programs%20not%20aligned%20with%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20First%26quot%3B%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20review%20in%20part%20targeted%20multi-year%20foreign%20assistance%20contracts%20awarded%20by%20the%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20(USAID)%2C%20with%20the%20vast%20majority%20eliminated%20during%20its%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20conclusion%20of%20a%20process%20led%20by%20USAID%20leadership%2C%20including%20tranches%20personally%20reviewed%20by%20Secretary%20(Marco)%20Rubio%2C%20nearly%205%2C800%20awards%20with%20%2454%20billion%20in%20value%20remaining%20were%20identified%20for%20elimination%20as%20part%20of%20the%20America%20First%20agenda%20--%20a%2092%20percent%20reduction%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20review%20also%20looked%20at%20more%20than%209%2C100%20grants%20involving%20foreign%20assistance%2C%20valued%20at%20more%20than%20%2415.9%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20review%2C%204%2C100%20grants%20worth%20almost%20%244.4%20billion%20were%20targeted%20to%20be%20eliminated%2C%20a%2028%20percent%20reduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20commonsense%20eliminations%20will%20allow%20the%20bureaus%2C%20along%20with%20their%20contracting%20and%20grants%20officers%2C%20to%20focus%20on%20remaining%20programs%2C%20find%20additional%20efficiencies%20and%20tailor%20subsequent%20programs%20more%20closely%20to%20the%20Administration's%20America%20First%20priorities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20State%20Department%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrograms%20that%20were%20not%20cut%20included%20food%20assistance%2C%20life-saving%20medical%20treatments%20for%20diseases%20like%20HIV%20and%20malaria%20and%20support%20for%20countries%20including%20Haiti%2C%20Cuba%2C%20Venezuela%20and%20Lebanon%2C%20among%20others%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20gave%20the%20Trump%20administration%20less%20than%20two%20days%20to%20unfreeze%20all%20aid%2C%20after%20a%20previous%20court%20order%20issued%20nearly%20two%20weeks%20earlier%20went%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20filed%20a%20petition%20to%20put%20a%20hold%20on%20the%20lower%20court%20order%2C%20which%20was%20granted%20by%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20John%20Roberts%20late%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20US%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSAID%2C%20created%20after%20a%20bill%20passed%20by%20Congress%20in%201961%2C%20had%20a%20workforce%20of%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20employees%20prior%20to%20the%20freeze%2C%20which%20sparked%20shock%20and%20dismay%20among%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20announced%20on%20February%2023%20that%20it%20was%20laying%20off%201%2C600%20of%20its%20employees%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20placing%20most%20of%20the%20remaining%20staff%20on%20administrative%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20election%20campaign%2C%20Trump%20promised%20to%20slash%20federal%20government%20spending%20and%20bureaucracy%2C%20a%20task%20he%20bestowed%20upon%20his%20top%20donor%20and%20close%20advisor%2C%20billionaire%20Elon%20Mu