%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20side%20dominated%20in%20all%20departments%20as%20India%20beat%20Pakistan%20by%20six%20wickets.%20But%20if%20a%20report%20is%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20fans%20may%20be%20up%20for%20three%20more%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20game%20later%20this%20year%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup.%20The%20continental%20extravaganza%2C%20which%20will%20be%20played%20in%20T20%20format%20this%20time%20around%2C%20will%20have%2019%20games%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20played%20between%20the%20second%20and%20fourth%20week%20of%20September%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cricbuzz.com%2Fcricket-news%2F133600%2Fmore-india-pakistan-games-on-the-horizon-as-asia-cup-gets-september-window%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202025%20was%20allotted%20to%20India%2C%20but%20given%20the%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20equation%2C%20the%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%20(ACC)%20has%20decided%20to%20host%20it%20in%20a%20neutral%20country.%20Though%20the%20venue%20is%20not%20final%2C%20the%20report%20said%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20UAE%20are%20likely%20options.%20BCCI%20will%20remain%20%C2%A0the%20designated%20hosts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%2C%20Pakistan%20are%20the%20designated%20hosts%20but%20India%20are%20not%20playing%20in%20the%20country%20after%20the%20BCCI%20refused%20to%20send%20its%20team.%20That%20lead%20to%20a%20big%20tussle%20between%20the%20two%20teams%20with%20India's%20matches%20being%20shifted%20to%20Dubai.%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BA%20key%20recent%20decision%20of%20the%20ACC%20was%20that%20the%20tournament%20be%20be%20held%20in%20a%20neutral%20country%20when%20it%20is%20the%20turn%20of%20either%20the%20BCCI%20or%20the%20PCB%20to%20stage%20it.%20A%20document%20in%20possession%20of%20this%20website%20states%20clearly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20decision%2C%20understandably%2C%20is%20to%20avoid%20any%20controversy%20about%20the%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20teams%20not%20wanting%20to%20travel%20to%20each%20other's%20countries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20teams%20-%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20UAE%2C%20Oman%2C%20and%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20besides%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20-%20will%20take%20part%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202025%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20Asia%20Cup%20is%20divided%20in%20two%20groups%20of%20four%20teams%20each.%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20are%20always%20kept%20in%20the%20same%20group.%20The%20top%20two%20teams%20from%20each%20group%20progress%20to%20the%20Super%20Four%20stage.%20The%20top%20two%20teams%20in%20Super%204%20then%20enter%20final.%20Generally%2C%20the%20groupings%20in%20Asia%20Cup%20are%20kept%20as%20such%20that%20there%20is%20high%20probability%20of%20at%20least%20two%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20matches.%20And%20a%20third%20one%2C%20if%20the%20two%20teams%20enter%20the%20final.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740679800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F6g4cbos8_india-pakistan_625x300_27_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmajor-blow-for-bcci-miss-out-on-hosting-three-india-vs-pakistan-matches-in-asia-cup-to-avoid-report-7808770%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20clash%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20was%20a%20pretty%20one-sided%20affair%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAt%20Super%20Speed%26quot%3B%3A%20Supriya%20Sule%20As%20Injured%20Student's%20Father%20Waits%20For%20US%20Visa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20visa%20request%20for%20the%20father%20of%20the%20injured%20Indian%20student%2C%20who%20is%20in%20coma%20in%20a%20US%20hospital%2C%20must%20be%20proces