tude%20towards%20MEA%20and%20the%20US%20embassy%20in%20Mumbai%20who%20have%20really%20helped%20us.%20I%20am%20eternally%20grateful...%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20MEA%20has%20helped%20us.%20There%20have%20been%20many%2C%20many%20instances%20where%20family%20and%20children%20have%20needed%20attention%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20gone%20out%20of%20its%20way%20and%20helped%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Sule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20from%20the%20university%20-%20issued%20February%2016%20-%20said%20Ms%20Shinde%20%26quot%3Bis%20in%20critical%20condition%20with%20an%20uncertain%20prognosis%20and%20is%20receiving%20care%20in%20the%20Intensive%20Care%20Unit%26quot%3B.%20The%20university%20added%20its%20appeal%20for%20travel%20permits%20to%20be%20issued%20for%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EVisa%20mil%20jaaye%20bus%20itna%20hi%20aur%20udhar%20jaa%20sake%20hum%3C%2Fem%3E%20(We%20just%20hope%20to%20get%20the%20visa%20and%20go%20to%20America)%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20emotional%20Tanaji%20Shinde%2C%20father%20of%20Nilam%20Shinde%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740679560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F7ce7lmgg_sule-marya-_625x300_27_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneed-it-at-super-speed-supriya-sule-as-injured-students-father-waits-for-us-visa-7810677%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20visa%20request%20for%20the%20father%20of%20the%20injured%20Indian%20student%2C%20who%20is%20in%20coma%20in%20a%20US%20hospital%2C%20must%20be%20processed%20at%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20speed%26quot%3B%2C%20urged%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Failed%20To%20%26quot%3BImagine%20Scenario%26quot%3B%20Like%20Oct%207%3A%20Israel%20Army%20Probe%20On%20Hamas%20Attack%22%2C%22content