Taking%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Ganga%20will%20not%20wash%20away%20the%20sin%20of%20betraying%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20president%20said%20on%20Thursday%20attacking%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20party%20event%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Marathi%20Bhasha%20Gaurav%20Diwas%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20also%20mounted%20a%20veiled%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP%20saying%20neo-Hindutvawadis%20need%20not%20teach%20his%20party%20the%20importance%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20respect%20the%20Ganga%20but%20what%20is%20the%20use%20of%20taking%20a%20dip%20in%20it%20after%20taking%2050%20khokas%20(street%20lingo%20for%20crore).%20Here%2C%20you%20betray%20Maharashtra%2C%20take%2050%20khokas%20and%20then%20you%20take%20a%20dip.%20This%20does%20not%20wash%20anyone's%20sin.%20How%20will%20the%20tag%20of%20being%20a%20betrayer%20go%20even%20after%20numerous%20dips%20(in%20the%20Ganga)%2C%26quot%3B%20Thackeray%20said%20without%20naming%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20split%20in%202022%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20accused%20Shinde%20and%2039%20MLAs%20of%20taking%2050%20khokas%20(Rs%2050%20crore%20each)%20to%20revolt%20against%20the%20Sena%20leadership.%20Shinde's%20rebellion%20led%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20Thackeray-led%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShinde%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20MLAs%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20in%20Prayagraj%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Shinde%20had%20taken%20a%20dig%20at%20Thackeray%20for%20not%20attending%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20and%20said%20the%20latter%20was%20scared%20of%20calling%20himself%20a%20Hindu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20skipped%20Maha%20Kumbh%20should%20be%20asked%20why%20they%20skipped%20it.%20They%20keep%20saying%20they%20are%20Hindus.%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray%20proudly%20gave%20the%20slogan%20'garv%20se%20kaho%20hum%20Hindu%20