quot%3BI%20have%20proof%20from%20all%20districts.%20Here%20it%20is.%20Names%20of%20people%20from%20Haryana%20and%20Gujarat%20appear%20alongside%20those%20of%20West%20Bengal%20residents%20under%20the%20same%20EPIC%20(Election%20Photo%20Identity%20Card)%20number.%20Fake%20voters%20have%20been%20added%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee%20directed%20TMC%20leaders%20and%20workers%20to%20immediately%20start%20verifying%20the%20voter%20list%20at%20the%20booth%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDistrict%20presidents%20should%20oversee%20the%20process%20and%20submit%20their%20findings%20within%20seven%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20TMC%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20tasked%20TMC%20state%20president%20Subrata%20Bakshi%20with%20leading%20a%20committee%20comprising%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20MP%20Sudip%20Bandyopadhyay%20and%20other%20senior%20leaders%20to%20examine%20the%20voter%20list%20across%20all%20blocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20verification%20process%20will%20commence%20on%20Friday%20and%20must%20be%20completed%20within%2010%20days%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20could%20go%20on%20a%2026-day%20hunger%20strike%20during%20the%20anti-land%20acquisition%20movement%20in%202006%2C%20we%20can%20also%20launch%20a%20movement%20against%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20restore%20democracy.%20If%20required%2C%20we%20will%20protest%20indefinitely%20in%20front%20of%20the%20EC%20office%20to%20demand%20the%20removal%20of%20fake%20names%20from%20the%20voter%20roll%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee%20also%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20appointment%20of%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%20as%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20respect%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20But%20now%2C%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20filled%20with%20BJP-aligned%20individuals.%20The%20new%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%2C%20previously%20worked%20as%20a%20secretary%20in%20the%20cooperation%20department%20under%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister.%20It%20is%20evident%20how%20the%20BJP%20is%20tampering%20with%20the%20voter%20list%20with%20the%20blessings%20of%20the%20EC%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee%20claimed%20that%20this%20is%20the%20way%20the%20BJP%20won%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Delhi%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20after%20Maharashtra%20and%20Delhi%2C%20they%20are%20targeting%20West%20Bengal.%20We%20will%20respond%20strongly.%20Khela%20Abar%20Hobe%20(the%20game%20is%20on%20again).%20I%20urge%20workers%20to%20strike%20back%20even%20harder%20this%20time.%20In%20Bengal%2C%20we%20will%20take%20them%20head-on.%20By%202027-2029%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20be%20finished.%20They%20have%20only%202-3%20years%20left%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKhela%20Hobe%26quot%3B%20(the%20game%20is%20on)%20was%20the%20battle%20cry%20of%20the%20TMC%20during%20the%20high-octane%202021%20assembly%20polls%20when%20the%20party%20defeated%20the%20BJP%20to%20storm%20back%20to%20power%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutlining%20the%20TMC's%20electoral%20strategy%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20the%20first%20priority%20would%20be%20cleaning%20up%20the%20voter%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20game%20is%20to%20fix%20the%20fraudulent%20voter%20lists.%20Game%20number%202%20is%20establishing%20direct%20connections%20with%20people%20by%20visiting%20them%20at%20their%20doorsteps.%20Game%20number%203%20is%20strengthening%20the%20organisation%20and%20being%20vigilant%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%20chief%20asked%20party%20workers%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20who%20is%20coming%20to%20the%20area%20and%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20ensure%20that%20our%20harmony%20is%20preserved%20and%20no%20person%20is%20tortured.%20Game%20number%204%20will%20be%20BJP's%20defeat.%20The%20BJP%20should%20not%20even%20get%20the%20numbers%20they%20did%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20countered%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20allegations%2C%20claiming%20she%20was%20attempting%20to%20galvanise%20party%20workers%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20losing%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20world%20knows%20TMC%20for%20its%20mastery%20in%20electoral%20malpractices%20and%20vote%20loot.%20Hindus%20in%20Bengal%20have%20united%2C%20and%20that%20is%20why%20she%20is%20scared%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20MP%20Samik%20Bhattacharya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20won%2077%20seats%20in%20the%202021%20assembly%20elections%2C%20while%20the%20TMC%20secured%20213%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740675120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fvok7s2io_mamata-banerjee_625x300_27_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flike-delhi-maharashtra-mamata-banerjees-big-poll-charge-against-bjp-7810187%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Setting%20the%20stage%20for%20next%20year's%202026%20assembly%20elections%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20on%20Thursday%20set%20an%20ambitious%20target%20of%20winning%20over%20215%20of%20the%20294%20assembly%20seats%20to%20secure%20a%20fourth%20consecutive%20term%20in%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gene%20Hackman%20and%20Wife%E2%80%99s%20Death%20Ruled%20%E2%80%98Suspicious%E2%80%99%20in%20Search%20Warrant%3A%20%E2%80%98No%20Obvious%20Signs%20of%20a%20Gas%20Leak%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Thorough%20Investigation%E2%80%99%20Required%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740675041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FGettyImages-2154022001.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236322610%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20deaths%20of%20actor%20Gene%20Hackman%20and%20his%20wife%20Betsy%20Arakawa%20have%20been%20ruled%20%E2%80%9Csuspicious%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20a%20search%20warrant%20affidavit%20released%20Thursday%20morning.%20Hackman%2C%2095%2C%20and%20Arakawa%2C%2063%2C%20were%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20home%20in%20Santa%20Fe%2C%20N.M.%2C%20after%20midnight%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Santa%20Fe%20County%20Sheriff%20had%20confirmed%20to%20Variety.%20Authorities%20said%20there%20was%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Jordan%20Moreau%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fgene-hackman-death-suspicious-gas-leak-search-warrant-1236322610%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Volcanic%20Eruption%20In%2079%20AD%20Turned%20Man's%20Brain%20Into%20Glass.%20How%20It%20Happened%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20surprising%20discovery%20when%20scientists%20examining%20the%20remains%20of%20a%20man%20who%20died%20in%20bed%20in%20the%20ancient%20city%20of%20Herculaneum%20after%20Italy's%20Mount%20Vesuvius%20erupted%20in%2079%20AD%20found%20dark%20fragments%20resembling%20obsidian%20inside%20his%20skull.%20It%20turns%20out%20the%20eruption%20had%20somehow%20turned%20his%20brain%20into%20glass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20only%20case%20on%20record%20of%20such%20a%20phenomenon%2C%20and%20researchers%20now%20have%20answers%20for%20why%20and%20how%20it%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20say%20the%20vitrification%20-%20transformation%20into%20glass%20-%20of%20this%20victim's%20brain%20was%20the%20apparent%20effect%20of%20a%20scorching%20ash%20cloud%20that%20suddenly%20descended%20upon%20his%20city%20along%20the%20Bay%20of%20Naples%2C%20instantly%20killing%20all%20the%20inhabitants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20concluded%20vitrification%20took%20place%20through%20a%20unique%20process%20of%20rapid%20exposure%20of%20the%20brain's%20organic%20material%20to%20a%20very%20high%20temperature%20-%20at%20least%20510%20degrees%20Celsius%20(950%20degrees%20F)%20-%20and%20its%20subsequent%20rapid%20cooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20conducted%20an%20extensive%20analysis%20that%20confirmed%20the%20glass%20nature%20of%20the%20fragments%20and%20revealed%20their%20physical%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20glass%20formed%20as%20a%20result%20of%20this%20process%20allowed%20for%20an%20integral%20preservation%20of%20the%20biological%20brain%20material%20and%20its%20microstructures%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20forensic%20anthropologist%20Pier%20Paolo%20Petrone%20of%20Universita%20di%20Napoli%20Federico%20II%20in%20Italy%2C%20one%20of%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20research%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Scientific%20Reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eruption%20obliterated%20the%20thriving%20ancient%20Roman%20cities%20of%20Pompeii%20and%20Herculaneum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20other%20type%20of%20organic%20glass%20we%20have%20evidence%20of%20is%20that%20produced%20in%20some%20rare%20cases%20of%20vitrification%20of%20wood%2C%20sporadic%20cases%20of%20which%20have%20been%20found%20at%20Herculaneum%20and%20Pompeii.%20However%2C%20in%20no%20other%20case%20in%20the%20world%20have%20vitrified%20organic%20human%20or%20animal%20remains%20ever%20been%20found%2C%26quot%3B%20Petrone%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20the%20two%20cities%20were%20buried%20under%20a%20thick%20layer%20of%20volcanic%20material%20and%20mud%2C%20sitting%20untouched%20until%20their%20rediscovery%20in%20the%2018th%20century.%20Victims%20were%20preserved%20in%20sudden%20death%2C%20as%20was%20the%20case%20with%20the%20one%20whose%20brain%20was%20turned%20to%20glass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20body%20was%20first%20discovered%20in%20the%201960s%20inside%20a%20building%20called%20the%20College%20of%20the%20Augustales%20dedicated%20to%20the%20cult%20of%20Emperor%20Augustus%2C%20who%20had%20died%20in%2014%20AD.%20The%20individual%20was%20identified%20as%20a%20young%20man%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20the%20college's%20custodian.%20The%20remains%20were%20re-examined%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20the%20room%20where%20the%20college's%20custodian%20was%20lying%20in%20his%20bed%20to%20document%20his%20charred%20bones.%20Under%20the%20lamp%2C%20I%20suddenly%20saw%20small%20glassy%20remains%20glittering%20in%20the%20volcanic%20ash%20that%20filled%20the%20skull%2C%26quot%3B%20Petrone%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20one%20of%20these%20fragments%2C%20it%20had%20a%20black%20appearance%20and%20shiny%20surfaces%20quite%20similar%20to%20obsidian%2C%20a%20natural%20glass%20of%20volcanic%20origin%20-%20black%20and%20shiny%2C%20whose%20formation%20is%20due%20to%20the%20very%20rapid%20cooling%20of%20the%20lava.%20But%2C%20unlike%20obsidian%2C%20the%20glassy%20remains%20were%20extremely%20brittle%20and%20easy%20to%20crumble%2C%26quot%3B%20Petrone%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalyses%20of%20this%20material%2C%20previously%20published%20in%20other%20scientific%20journals%2C%20revealed%20the%20presence%20of%20proteins%20and%20fatty%20acids%20common%20in%20human%20brain%20tissues%2C%20with%20the%20entire%20central%20nervous%20system%20exceptionally%20well%20preserved%2C%20represented%20by%20nerve%20cells%20interconnected%20by%20a%20dense%20network%20of%20fibers%20called%20axons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20is%20forging%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20how%20the%20tragic%20events%20unfolded%20after%20the%20eruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20study%20shows%20that%20the%20'killer'%20at%20Herculaneum%20was%20the%20arrival%20in%20town%20of%20an%20early%20hot%20ash%20cloud.%20This%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20understanding%20the%20behavior%20of%20ash%20clouds%2C%20as%20they%20are%20very%20hazardous%20and%20still%20very%20poorly%20studied%20and%20understood%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20volcanologist%20and%20study%20first%20author%20Guido%20Giordano%20of%20Roma%20Tre%20University%20in%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actual%20burial%20of%20the%20city%20occurred%20in%20later%20stages%20of%20the%20eruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20custodian%20at%20apparently%20around%20midnight%20was%20surprised%20while%20sleeping%20in%20his%20bed%20by%20the%20first%20effects%20of%20the%20eruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20postures%20of%20the%20victims'%20bodies%20show%2C%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20college%20died%20instantly%20from%20the%20impact%20with%20the%20hot%20volcanic%20ash%20surge%2C%20as%20did%20all%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20inhabitants%20of%20Herculaneum%2C%26quot%3B%20Petrone%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20body%20of%20evidence%20found%20for%20the%20victims%20at%20Herculaneum%20shows%20that%20all%20people%20died%20instantly%2C%20so%20they%20did%20not%20have%20time%20to%20notice%20or%20suffer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740675000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fgeb9q1u8_mount-vesuvius_625x300_27_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fitalys-mount-vesuvius-volcanic-eruption-in-79-ad-turned-mans-brain-into-glass-how-it-happened-7810184%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20a%20surprising%20discovery%20when%20scientists%20examining%20the%20remains%20of%20a%20man%20who%20died%20in%20bed%20in%20the%20ancient%20city%20of%20Herculaneum%20after%20Italy's%20Mount%20Vesuvius%20erupted%20in%2079%20AD%20fou