oughout%20the%20year.%20The%20water%20hole%20ideally%20needs%20to%20be%20filled%20up%20once%20a%20week%20and%20during%20hot%20summers%20once%20in%202-3%20days.%20We%20were%20earlier%20dependent%20on%20water%20tankers.%20On%20a%20rough%20estimate%2C%20we%20now%20save%20about%20Rs%2030%2C000%20per%20year%20for%20each%20water%20hole%20because%20of%20these%20solar-pump-based%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20CSR%20backing%20by%20corporations%20and%20funds%20raised%20by%20generous%20benefactors%2C%20the%20couple%20continues%20to%20carve%20the%20path%20forward.%20Dr%20Sarita%20mentions%20that%20it%20costs%20them%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20support%20a%20solar-powered%20water%20pump%20in%20a%20given%20forest%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%20of%20working%20in%20remote%20and%20often%20inaccessible%20areas%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20been%20tirelessly%20advocating%20for%20the%20seamless%20integration%20of%20clean%20energy%20and%20wildlife%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDFcLh-Jv2Me%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDFcLh-Jv2Me%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%