20transitioning%20red%20pandas%20from%20reliance%20on%20artificial%20food%20to%20a%20diet%20primarily%20consisting%20of%20natural%20resources.%20Once%20the%20red%20pandas%20have%20successfully%20acclimatised%20to%20a%20natural%20diet%2C%20they%20are%20released%20into%20the%20wild.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBiobank%20and%20genetic%20research%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarring%20externalities%20such%20as%20predators%20and%20poaching%2C%20an%20internal%20factor%20that%20has%20also%20contributed%20to%20the%20decline%20in%20red%20panda%20numbers%20is%20their%20nature.%20Red%20pandas%20are%20solitary%20creatures%20and%20prone%20to%20gene-related%20diseases%20due%20to%20inbreeding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGenetic%20diversity%20is%20the%20fundamental%20building%20block%20of%20a%20population%2C%20which%20means%20that%20the%20health%20of%20the%20population%20is%20dictated%20by%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Karthikeyan%20Vasudevan%2C%20chief%20scientist%20for%20LaCONES%20(Laboratory%20for%20the%20Conservation%20of%20Endangered%20Species)%2C%20an%20annexure%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Cellular%20and%20Molecular%20Biology%20(CCMB).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20like%20a%20Swiss%20army%20knife.%20You%20can%20do%20many%20things%20with%20it.%20If%20you%20have%20many%20tools%20in%20your%20genetic%20constitution%2C%20then%20you%20have%20a%20better%20ability%20to%20deal%20with%20diseases%2C%20anything%20that%20might%20happen%20to%20the%20population%20due%20to%20some%20infection%20and%20sudden%20climatic%20and%20natural%20disaster%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20where%20the%20zoo%E2%80%99s%20genetic%20biobank%20comes%20into%20play.%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20individuals%20we%20are%20releasing%2C%20proper%20genetic%20analysis%20is%20being%20done%20through%20scientific%20institutions%20like%20CCMB.%20We%20release%20individuals%20with%20high%20genetic%20diversity%20and%20heterozygosity.%20That%20contributes%20to%20the%20genetic%20makeup%20of%20the%20population%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Holeyachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGenetic%20resources%20like%20DNA%2C%20RNA%2C%20sperms%2C%20oocytes%2C%20or%20any%20other%20bodily%20tissues%20are%20valuable%20and%20can%20be%20biobanked.%20Preserved%20in%20liquid%20nitrogen%20at%C2%A0%20-196%20deg%20C%2C%20they%20can%20remain%20alive%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Vasudevan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Karthikeyan%20Vasudevan%2C%20Chief%20Scientist%20from%20LaCONES%20lab%2C%20CCMB%20conducted%20the%20training%20program%20for%20the%20officials%20%26amp%3B%20staffs%20of%20PNHZP%20%26amp%3B%20Bengal%20Safari%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961-768x511.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-407796%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22719%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Karthikeyan%20Vasudevan%2C%20Chief%20Scientist%20from%20LaCONES%20lab%2C%20CCMB%20conducted%20the%20training%20programme%20for%20the%20officials%20and%20staff%20of%20PNHZP%20%26amp%3B%20Bengal%20Safari%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiobanking%20of%20endangered%20species%20is%20gaining%20popularity%20across%20the%20world%20as%20a%20promising%20conservation%20tool.%20Apart%20from%20providing%20invaluable%20information%20that%20could%20aid%20in%20understanding%20susceptibility%2C%20reproductive%20success%2C%20and%20adaptation%20to%20environmental%20change%2C%20biobank%20gametes%20(sperm%20and%20eggs)%20can%20be%20used%20for%20assisted%20reproductive%20technologies%20like%20artificial%20insemination%20or%20in%20vitro%20fertilisation%20(IVF).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTypically%20you%20can%20equate%20an%20endangered%20species%20to%20a%20person%20in%20an%20ICU.%20To%20help%20that%20person%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20have%20to%20give%20some%20support%2C%20put%20in%20some%20monitors%2C%20conduct%20tests%2C%20and%20check%2C%20and%20then%20give%20the%20possible%20best%20treatment%20so%20that%20that%20person%20recovers.%20This%20is%20exactly%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20with%20endangered%20species%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Vasudevan%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20bringing%20it%2C%20making%20sure%20we%20provide%20everything%20to%20ensure%20it%20successfully%20increases%20in%20numbers%20and%20can%20be%20given%20a%20home%20in%20the%20wild%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaCONES%20also%20helps%20Darjeeling%20Zoo%20plan%20its%20conservation%20breeding%20programmes%20by%20screening%20animals%20for%20diseases%20and%20providing%20information%20on%20the%20founder%20populations%E2%80%99%20genetic%20makeup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20holistic%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20animals%20have%20a%20generation%20time%20%E2%80%94%20the%20period%20from%20birth%20to%20when%20they%20reach%20sexual%20maturity%20and%20produce%20their%20offspring.%20For%20red%20pandas%2C%20this%20is%2018-20%20months.%20But%20in%20the%20wild%2C%20numerous%20constraints%20impact%20this%20process%3A%20high%20mortality%20rates%20among%20the%20young%2C%20challenges%20in%20finding%20mates%2C%20potential%20food%20shortages%20after%20pregnancy%2C%20and%20predation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptive%20breeding%20programmes%20aim%20to%20mitigate%20these%20challenges%20by%20providing%20a%20controlled%20environment%20with%20adequate%20food%20and%20protection%20from%20predators%2C%20and%20by%20carefully%20selecting%20breeding%20pairs%20to%20maximise%20genetic%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Darjeeling%20Zoo%20was%20shortlisted%20for%20the%20WAZA%20Conservation%20and%20Environmental%20Sustainability%20Awards%20in%202024%20for%20its%20red%20panda%20conservation%20efforts%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-407798%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDarjeeling%20Zoo%20was%20shortlisted%20for%20the%20WAZA%20Conservation%20and%20Environmental%20Sustainability%20Awards%20in%202024%20for%20its%20red%20panda%20conservation%20efforts%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20even%20if%20you%20have%20seven%20individuals%2C%20you%20can%20bring%20its%20numbers%20up%20by%20actually%20planning%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20slowly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Vasudevan.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20these%20things%20don%E2%80%99t%20happen%20immediately.%20Sometimes%20it%20takes%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20shadow%20of%20the%20majestic%20Himalayas%2C%20the%20red%20panda%20is%20not%20just%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20natural%20beauty%2C%20but%20also%20a%20barometer%20of%20the%20health%20of%20its%20fragile%20ecosystems.%20As%20Dr%20Holeyachi%20aptly%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ecosystem%20is%20an%20intricate%20and%20interconnected%20system%20where%20every%20species%20relies%20on%20others.%20Red%20pandas%20play%20a%20vital%20role%20within%20this%20ecosystem.%20By%20protecting%20red%20pandas%2C%20conservationists%20are%20simultaneously%20safeguarding%20their%20habitat%20and%20the%20diverse%20array%20of%20species%20that%20coexist%20within%20it.%20This%20integrated%20approach%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20long-term%20conservation%20of%20the%20entire%20ecosystem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Megha%20Chowdhury%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%20Padmaja%20Naidu%20Himalayan%20Zoological%20Park%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740400200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-19-at-18.18.21_11zon-1740103390.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D407782%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20its%20fiery%20red%20coat%2C%20masked%20face%2C%20and%20ringed%20tail%2C%20the%20red%20panda%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20creature%20out%20of%20a%20storybook.%20Yet%2C%20in%20the%20wilds%20of%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20